      "BookmanOldStyle-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      96.02,
      298.59,
      526.68,
      312.65
    ],
    "text": "(ii) The essence of a judgment consists in the reason for conviction of",
